"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*eK3Yxnrx9wN-1YHcDnPLCg.png)\\n\\nWePiggy 2021/7/9 product updates are as follows:\\n\\n## For Desktop&Mobile（All networks）\\n\\n## **1. Add \\\\[Security\\\\] Page**\\n\\nPage link: <https://wepiggy.com/security>\\n\\nWePiggy is committed to creating a safe, open and transparent decentralized financial ecosystem. The realization of this goal is inseparable from the joint efforts of the WePiggy core development team and the community.\\n\\nTo show WePiggy’s layout and considerations at the security level, and deepen WePiggy’s security-focused image in the minds of community users, WePiggy has now launched the “Security” page.\\n\\nThis page includes the following sections:\\n\\n***Open-Source Code Repository***\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*gC_pQNBwZ_3z-f8B.png)\\n\\n***Eight Security Modules***\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*XtoVQVIVCrL3bD1U.png)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*EEYnp3gAexbTSnyn.png)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*Iz8Zkx2x77PEm_nD.png)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*gBeWMqNwv_wnAo0N.png)\\n\\n***Bug Bounty Program***\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*MnqzqxE4fAyTNWnB.png)\\n\\n## **2. \\\\[Navigation Bar\\\\] Optimization**\\n\\nOptimize the navigation bar styleAdd \\\\[Switch Network\\\\] buttonAdd \\\\[Bottom Bar\\\\]Add \\\\[Cross-Chain Bridge\\\\] in the sidebar\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*bzph7FWdtlFzmbu-.png)\\n\\n## **3. \\\\[NFT Gallery\\\\] Optimization**\\n\\nAdd back silhouettes for all NFTs\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*QT73NKHq4zy5r5GE.png)\\n\\n## **4. \\\\[Homepage\\\\] Optimization**\\n\\nOptimize the top and bottom columns\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*RjCSBC1fa2-EJPDI.png)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*qeWv_S1Fjpcjfyl7.png)\\n\\n## **5. Update \\\\[Used Ratio\\\\] Term Explanation**\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/798/0\\\\*mimdx1-kWJyRIIve.png)\\n\\n## **6. Optimize the Repayment Process**\\n\\n## **7. Optimize the Entrance of the WePiggy’s Billionaires**\\n\\n## **8. Speed Up the Transaction Speed, Change the Confirmation Block from 2 to 1**\",\"timestamp\":1636596590,\"title\":\"WePiggy Product Updates and New Page “Security” Goes Live\"},\"digest\":\"Ug0R3N9i8azKEdW3_TJtnUaO89bcH6ybeQTocJHMPYI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MOToXuaua0SJZ5_SQSsecHvAOLw5KxmLTKhH_Amk1Lw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eHu9Uej8BHwgyRn4jxCzG9EQ1R29cSjilBrFY8fm7pw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"PKLFLpzfTB7A5MrgKApC8cUFuf4fa7m3yBNWkHwvRcdSo9fUWJx8N0c3e65COsqk2YgzxJNzGYS55wAGqAceMw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc82d064579e95fce57e72d8f3e37759f40fd261e5df790f87edb0ce708ab9b09088a8d04cbf29e5ca12f34f0b482a37f2f71c105a2ea08c50f6161ee26251fa01b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MOToXuaua0SJZ5_SQSsecHvAOLw5KxmLTKhH_Amk1Lw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eHu9Uej8BHwgyRn4jxCzG9EQ1R29cSjilBrFY8fm7pw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Ug0R3N9i8azKEdW3_TJtnUaO89bcH6ybeQTocJHMPYI\"}"